                                    <cell rendition="#nowrap">Greece, Philippines</cell>
                                    <cell>Greece<note n="*" xml:id="d50fn2">US disposed to support
                                            Greece as long as it is the candidate on which there is
                                            reasonable prospect of securing widest agreement in
                                                <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss>. [Footnote in the
                                            source text.]</note>
                                    </cell>
